query:
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO market_caps (
                            ticker, name, market_cap_original, original_currency,
                            market_cap_eur, market_cap_usd, eur_rate, usd_rate,
                            exchange, price, active, timestamp
                        )
                        VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
